# Inventory Management System Project (Components)

## Features

User Authentication
- Registration and Login
- Google OAuth for seamless login

Shop Management
- Shop Creation
- Initial Product Limit (3 products)

Subscription-based Offers
- Monthly Subscriptions
- Payment through Stripe
- Increased Product Limit for Subscribers

Product Management
- Add, Update, Delete Products

Dashboard
- Total Sales Information
- Total Profit Details
- Total Costing Insights
- Sales Chart by Employee
- Recently Sold Products

## Technology Used
- React (JavaScript library for UI)
- React Router (Declarative routing)
- SQLite (Database system for structured data storage)
